Author: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Feb 11 11:58:44 2025 +0200

    Fix Nullability for array_position
    
    Remove `STRICTNULL` from `array_position` as with the flag it returns
    wrong results when used on the `WHERE` clause on a table cols wrapped
    with the `NOT` predicate.
    
    Fixes: #17378
    (cherry picked from commit f0f7f5051a75eb1362ae76f83a5e63db3d94b7e3)
    
    # Conflicts:
    #       docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.1.rst

